data.description: This charming 1920-built home in Fort Wayne, IN is a great investment property opportunity. The house features 3 spacious bedrooms and 1.5 baths, perfect for a small family or as a rental property. The windows have been updated, which is a great bonus. The dry basement provides additional storage space. The detached 2-car garage is more like a small pole, providing ample space for parking and storage.  Although the property needs some Tender Love Care, it holds a timeless take on modern living. With some renovation, this property can be transformed into a beautiful home.
